cff-version: 1.2.0
type: software
title: "Visual Oracle Bench — Multi-Application Empirical Evaluation of LLM-as-Judge Visual Regression Detection"
abstract: >-
  Companion software, datasets, and analysis pipeline for the Empirical
  Software Engineering submission "Beyond TodoMVC: A Multi-Application
  Empirical Evaluation of LLM-as-Judge Visual Regression Detection Across
  8 Open-Source Web Applications." Includes the 6-primitive defect-injection
  library, per-app capture orchestrator across 8 OSS web apps, pixel SSIM
  and perceptual-hash oracles, and LLM-as-judge wrappers for four vision
  models (GPT, Claude Sonnet 4.5, Gemini 2.5 Pro, Llama 3.2 Vision) with
  both API-key and OAuth/subscription access paths.
